title: Grateful Dead Live at Alpine Valley Music Theatre on 1988-06-23

description:
Set 1

Iko Iko, Minglewood Blues, It Must Have Been The Roses, Me & My Uncle-> Mexicali Blues, Stagger Lee, When I Paint My Masterpiece, Bird Song, Promised Land

Set 2

Hey Pocky Way, Believe It Or Not, Women Are Smarter, He's Gone-> Drums-> Jam-> I Need A Miracle-> Gimme Some Lovin'-> All Along The Watchtower-> Morning Dew, E:Blackbird-> E: Brokedown Palace

First GD Performance Of "Blackbird"

reviews.review_text: Immaculate Dew Crazy hot summer but well worth it. Morning Dew just brought a calm and awe over the place like only The Grateful Dead's magic could do. God Bless The Dead
